 on yourself.&nbsp;<a href='/s/40993.html' target='blank' title='into the page of the sentence'><img src='/images/enter.jpg' style='vertical-align:bottom'/></a></div><div>10. My fellow Americans, ask not what your country can do for <em>you</em>; ask what you can do for your country. My fellow citizens of the world ; ask not what America will do for you, but what together we can do for the freedom of man.&nbsp;<a href='/s/46854.html' target='blank' title='into the page of the sentence'><img src='/images/enter.jpg' style='vertical-align:bottom'/></a></div><div>11. If <em>you</em> want knwledge, you must toil for it.&nbsp;<a href='/s/43106.html' target='blank' title='into the page of the sentence'><img src='/images/enter.jpg' style='vertical-align:bottom'/></a></div><div>12. <em>You</em> cannot judge a tree by its bark.&nbsp;<a href='/s/44233.html' target='blank' title='into the page of the sentence'><img src='/images/enter.jpg' style='vertical-align:bottom'/></a></div><div>13. When the horse is stolen, (<em>you</em>) lock the stable door.&nbsp;<a href='/s/42282.html' target='blank' title='into the page of the sentence'><img src='/images/enter.jpg' style='vertical-align:bottom'/></a></div><div>14. <em>You</em> can’t touch pitch without being defiled.&nbsp;<a href='/s/42366.html' target='blank' title='into the page of the sentence'><img src='/images/enter.jpg' style='vertical-align:bottom'/></a></div><div>15. If <em>you</em> can't stand the heat get out of the kitchen.&nbsp;<a href='/s/47969.html' target='blank' title='into the page of the sentence'><img src='/images/enter.jpg' style='vertical-align:bottom'/></a></div><div>16. Love as in time to come <em>you</em> should hate, and hate as you should in time to come(sentencedict.com), love.&nbsp;<a href='/s/42378.html' target='blank' title='into the page of the sentence'><img src='/images/enter.jpg' style='vertical-align:bottom'/></a></div><div>17. I tell <em>you</em> hopeless grief is passionless.&nbsp;<a href='/s/46963.html' target='blank' title='into the page of the sentence'><img src='/images/enter.jpg' style='vertical-align:bottom'/></a></div><div>18. If they say <em>you</em> are good, ask yourself if it be true.&nbsp;<a href='/s/41190.html' target='blank' title='into the page of the sentence'><img src='/images/enter.jpg' style='vertical-align:bottom'/></a></div><div>19. Grasp the nettle and it won't sting <em>you</em>.&nbsp;<a href='/s/42887.html' target='blank' title='into the page of the sentence'><img src='/images/enter.jpg' style='vertical-align:bottom'/></a></div><div>20. I disapprove of what <em>you</em> say, but I will defend to the death your right to say it.&nbsp;<a href='/s/46995.html' target='blank' title='into the page of the sentence'><img src='/images/enter.jpg' style='vertical-align:bottom'/></a></div><div>21. Do not to others what <em>you</em> do not wish them to do to you.&nbsp;<a href='/s/42727.html' target='blank' title='into the page of the sentence'><img src='/images/enter.jpg' style='vertical-align:bottom'/></a></div><div>22. <em>You</em> win some, you lose some.&nbsp;<a href='/s/48177.html' target='blank' title='into the page of the sentence'><img src='/images/enter.jpg' style='vertical-align:bottom'/></a></div><div>23. <em>You</em> can't have your cake and eat it.&nbsp;<a href='/s/48166.html' target='blank' title='into the page of the sentence'><img src='/images/enter.jpg' style='vertical-align:bottom'/></a></div><div>24. <em>You</em> may delay[sentencedict.com], but time will not.&nbsp;<a title='show the description of wikipedia' href='https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Benjamin Franklin' target='_blank'>Benjamin Franklin</a>&nbsp;<a href='/s/33265.html' target='blank' title='into the page of the sentence'><img src='/images/enter.jpg' style='vertical-align:bottom'/></a></div><div>25. If <em>you</em> want a thing done well, do it yourself.&nbsp;<a title='show the description of wikipedia' href='https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Napoleon Bonaparte' target='_blank'>Napoleon Bonaparte</a>&nbsp;<a href='/s/37621.html' target='blank' title='into the page of the sentence'><img src='/images/enter.jpg' style='vertical-align:bottom'/></a></div><div>26. <em>You</em> have no goats, and yet you sell kids.&nbsp;<a href='/s/42368.html' target='blank' title='into the page of the sentence'><img src='/images/enter.jpg' style='vertical-align:bottom'/></a></div><div>27. If <em>you</em> command wisely, you'll be obeyed cheerfully.&nbsp;<a title='show the description of wikipedia' href='https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Thomas Fuller' target='_blank'>Thomas Fuller</a>&nbsp;<a href='/s/39507.html' target='blank' title='into the page of the sentence'><img src='/images/enter.jpg' style='vertical-align:bottom'/></a></div><div>28. Never trouble trouble till trouble troubles <em>you</em>.&nbsp;<a href='/s/41570.html' target='blank' title='into the page of the sentence'><img src='/images/enter.jpg' style='vertical-align:bottom'/></a></div><div>29. Though <em>you</em> cast out nature with a fork, it will still return.&nbsp;<a href='/s/43997.html' target='blank' title='into the page of the sentence'><img src='/images/enter.jpg' style='vertical-align:bottom'/></a></div><div style="margin-bottom:3px;">30. As a modern parent, I know that it's not how much <em>you</em> give children those counts, it's the love and attention you shower on them.A caring attitude can not only save you a small fortune, but also even make you feel good about being tight-fisted and offering more care than presents.&nbsp;<a href='/s/193269.html' target='blank' title='into the page of the sentence'><img src='/images/enter.jpg' style='vertical-align:bottom'/></a></div></div><!--all结束-->  <!--如果不是仅显示学生,或该页没有学生句子-->  <div id="student" style='display:none;'>  <div>1. <em>You</em> can bank by phone in the USA, punching in account numbers on the phone.</div><div>2. Places are strictly limited, so <em>you</em> should apply as soon as possible.</div><div>3. Are <em>you</em> prepared to repea